story: Sophia and Liam were friends who loved exploring. One day, they went to an old library. Sophia found a quiet room in the back. It had a big red chair and a dusty lamp. She called Liam to see it, but he was busy looking at a book about dinosaurs. Sophia sat in the chair and pretended to be a queen. Liam finally came over and laughed. "You look funny," he said. Sophia smiled and said, "This is my throne room!" Liam shook his head and went back to his book. Sophia stayed in the quiet room, imagining adventures. She found an old map under the chair. It showed a treasure hidden in the library. Excited, she ran to tell Liam. Together, they followed the map. They searched behind shelves and under tables. In the end, the treasure was just a box of old cookies. Liam ate one and made a face. "Yuck!" he said. Sophia laughed but kept the map as a memory. They left the library, happy with their mini adventure.
